{"id":33888,"type":4,"name":"Cloud","image":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/cover/m/a9/b8/33888_yaa9Q.jpg","rating":{"total":33,"count":{"1":0,"2":1,"3":1,"4":0,"5":2,"6":10,"7":9,"8":10,"9":0,"10":0},"score":6.6},"summary":"《云》（Cloud），也被称为《云：游戏》，是一款由陈星汉设计的第三人称益智类电脑游戏，基于天气和大气的美。这是他的首款获奖作品。游戏在美国南加州大学的互动媒体部设计，美国艺电投资，使用了由学生开发的Bushido Engine。游戏中有独特的手绘艺术，以及非暴力和灵感来自高桥庆太《块魂》的奇思妙想。第一版《云》于2005年秋季在网站上提供免费下载。\r\n\r\n故事围绕着患哮喘的7岁儿童“君”展开。因为哮喘，他不能在没有医生许可的情况下离开病房，只能无聊的待在房间里。君忘记了“轻轻穿过云层的感觉”。“飞”是一个6岁的女孩，是君的朋友。飞让君闭上眼睛并告诉她他所看到的，君说他看到了一直延伸到地平线的云。游戏至此开始。","info":"<li><span>中文名: </span>云</li><li><span>遊戲設計師: </span><a href=\"/person/8857\">陈星汉</a></li><li><span>平台: </span>PC</li><li><span>游戏类型: </span>益智</li><li><span>游戏引擎: </span>Bushido Engine</li><li><span>游玩人数: </span>单人游戏</li><li><span>发行日期: </span>2005年10月24日</li><li><span>发行: </span>USC Interactive Media Division</li>","collection":{"wish":24,"collect":43,"dropped":2},"tags":[{"name":"PC","count":13},{"name":"陈星汉","count":11},{"name":"云","count":9},{"name":"治愈","count":8},{"name":"天空","count":7},{"name":"Thatgamecompany","count":4},{"name":"indie","count":4},{"name":"ACT","count":4},{"name":"PUZ","count":4},{"name":"独立游戏","count":3},{"name":"JenovaChen","count":1},{"name":"独立","count":1},{"name":"6★","count":1}],"staff":[{"id":8857,"image":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/crt/g/10/82/8857_prsn_zW1rk.jpg","name":"陈星汉","desc":"遊戲設計師"}],"relations":[{"id":1447,"image":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/cover/m/c9/30/1447_PK4Kq.jpg","title":"Flower","type":"其他","url":"https://bgm.tv/subject/1447"},{"id":2003,"image":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/cover/m/a5/91/2003_D8fQo.jpg","title":"flOw","type":"其他","url":"https://bgm.tv/subject/2003"},{"id":35871,"image":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/cover/m/c8/d0/35871_XZZYZ.jpg","title":"Journey","type":"其他","url":"https://bgm.tv/subject/35871"}],"like":[{"id":942,"name":"扫雷","image":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/cover/m/b5/5e/942_0usq3.jpg"},{"id":311,"name":"千与千寻","image":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/cover/m/9d/fc/311_GAg3x.jpg"},{"id":289,"name":"寒蝉鸣泣之时","image":"//lain.bgm.tv/p